sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Platform
    participant GW as Platform Ingress<br/>TLS Termination
    participant NG as NeMo Guardrails<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails Pipeline
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails Pipeline
    participant Embed as Embedding Provider<br/>(local or 443/TCP)
    participant LLM as LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails

    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer Token
    GW->>NG: Forward (HTTP/8000)<br/>Auth header preserved

    NG->>InputRails: Process input rails
    InputRails->>Embed: Get embeddings<br/>(similarity checks)
    Embed-->>InputRails: Vector embeddings
    InputRails->>LLM: Content safety check<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    LLM-->>InputRails: Safety result
    InputRails-->>NG: PASSED / BLOCKED

    alt Input PASSED
        NG->>LLM: Chat completion request<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        LLM-->>NG: LLM response

        NG->>OutputRails: Process output rails
        OutputRails->>LLM: Output safety check<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        LLM-->>OutputRails: Safety result
        OutputRails-->>NG: PASSED / MODIFIED / BLOCKED
    end

    NG-->>GW: JSON response
    GW-->>Client: Response (TLS)

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Guardrail Check Only (No LLM Generation)

    Client->>GW: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>Authorization: Bearer Token
    GW->>NG: Forward (HTTP/8000)

    NG->>InputRails: Validate messages against rails
    InputRails->>LLM: Content safety model<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    LLM-->>InputRails: Validation result
    InputRails-->>NG: RailsResult

    NG-->>GW: Status: PASSED / MODIFIED / BLOCKED
    GW-->>Client: Validation result

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 3: Embedding-based Guardrail Evaluation

    NG->>Embed: Generate embeddings<br/>(local FastEmbed or HTTPS/443)
    Embed-->>NG: Embeddings
    NG->>NG: Annoy Index lookup<br/>(nearest neighbor search)
    NG->>LLM: Similarity-based rail evaluation<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    LLM-->>NG: Evaluation result
